<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @contact.name %>,
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for reaching out to us. We appreciate your interest in Xcelyst and would like to assure you that we have received your message. We are excited to connect with you and provide the assistance you need.
    </p>
    <p>
      A member of our team will be in touch with you shortly using the contact details you provided:
    </p>
    <p>
      Email: <%= @to_email %> <br>
      Phone: <%= @contact.phone_number %>
    </p>
    <p>
      We value your business and are committed to delivering exceptional service. If for any reason you do not receive a response from us, please do not hesitate to reach out to us directly at info@xcelyst.com. We are here to assist you and ensure your needs are met.
    </p>
    <p>
      Once again, thank you for your interest in Xcelyst. We look forward to connecting with you soon and providing you with the information and support you require.
    </p>
    <%= render 'layouts/email_footer' %>
  </body>
</html>